OL,3,CJudgment expected in nurses'
OL,4,Ctransgender changing room case
OL,6,FJudgment is expected on Friday in the
OL,7,Flegal challenge brought by nurses over
OL,8,Fa transgender colleague's use of the
OL,9,Ffemale changing-rooms at work.
OL,11,FEight members of the Day Surgery Unit
OL,12,Fat Darlington Memorial Hospital
OL,13,Fbrought a claim against Durham and
OL,14,FDarlington NHS Foundation Trust after
OL,15,FRose Henderson, who was born male but
OL,16,Fidentifies as a woman, was allowed to
OL,17,Fuse the women's changing facilities.
