OL,3,CJudgment expected in nurses'
OL,4,Ctransgender changing room case
OL,6,FAn employment tribunal in Newcastle,
OL,7,Fheard evidence from the nurses, the
OL,8,Ftrust and Rose before the panel
OL,9,Fadjourned the proceedings in November
OL,10,Fto consider its findings.
OL,12,FThe nurses claim that Rose stared at
OL,13,Fcolleagues in the female changing-
OL,14,Frooms, repeatedly asked one of them
OL,15,Fwhy she was not getting changed and
OL,16,Fwalked round the room in boxer shorts.
