OL,6,FIn response, Rose told the panel: "I
OL,7,Fam not the individual (the claimants)
OL,8,Fhave painted me to be" and described
OL,9,Fhow "upsetting" it had been to see
OL,10,F"hordes of people" posting insults
OL,11,Fonline after the case came to public
OL,12,Fattention.
OL,14,FThe Darlington nurses, who have been
OL,15,Fsupported by the Christian Legal
OL,16,FCentre, brought a claim for indirect
OL,17,Fdiscrimination, harassment and
OL,18,Fvictimisation, saying the complaints
OL,19,Fwhich they raised with the trust in
OL,20,FJuly 2023 were "buried".
