OL,6,FThe judgment follows nurse Sandy
OL,7,FPeggie's partial victory last month in
OL,8,Fher claim against her employer, NHS
OL,9,FFife, after she complained about being
OL,10,Fforced to share changing facilities
OL,11,Fwith transgender doctor Beth Upton at
OL,12,FKirkcaldy's Victoria Hospital in
OL,13,FDecember 2023.
